    "Likewise, FlowGAT trained on mannitol performs better when tested in galactose than glycerol, despite the galactose graph being more dissimilar to the mannitol graph.",
    "These observations suggest that the generalization performance of FlowGAT results from its representation power rather than the similarity between the input graphs.",
    "Essential genes often encode proteins that play critical roles in cellular processes needed for growth.",
